{"title_page": "RLSY College Aurangabad", "text_new": "{{short description|degree college in Bihar}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date = March 2020}}\n{{Use Indian English|date = March 2020}}\n{{Infobox university\n| native_name = Ram Lakhan Singh Yadav College\n| image       =\n| motto       = \n| established = {{Start date and age|1971}}\n| affiliation = [[Magadh University]]\n| principal   = Dr. Vijay Kumar Sinha\n| address     = Yamuna Nagar Road (G.T Road) \n| city        = [[Aurangabad]]\n| state       = [[Bihar]]\n| country     = [[India]]\n| postalcode  = 824101\n| coordinates = \n| website     = {{URL|http://rlsycollegeaurangabad.in/}}\n}}\n'''RLSY College, Aurangabad''' also known as '''Ram Lakhan Singh Yadav College, Aurangabad''' is a degree college in [[Aurangabad district]]<ref>{{cite web|title=RLSY College|url=https://www.bhaskar.com/bihar/aurangabad/news/rlsy-college-principal39s-exit-020603-4076651.html|website=Bhaskar news|accessdate=9 March 2019}}</ref> of [[Bihar]], [[India]].It is a Constitute College of [[Magadh University]]<ref>{{cite web|title= constituent college|url=https://magadhuniversity.ac.in/list-of-constituent-colleges/|website=Magadh university}}</ref>. The college offers [[senior secondary education]] ,[[undergraduate degree]]s and [[Postgraduate degree]]s in arts, science and conducts some vocational courses.The college was established in 1971 by [[Ram Lakhan Singh Yadav]]<ref>{{cite web|title=establish history|url=https://schools.org.in/aurangabad-(bihar)/10340313303/ram-lakhan-singh-yadav-college-aurangabad.html|website=school org}}</ref>. It is a Constitute College of [[Magadh University]] [[Bodh Gaya]] in 1986.Concerned with freedom revolution and localized on the high-way (G.T. Road) and in the heart of district headquarter of Aurangabad, Ramlakhan Singh Yadav College, was established in 1971. Affected with political and social injustice, the establishment of Ramlakhan Singh Yadav College by the hands of backward class people. [[File:Yadav College.png|right|250px]]\n== Degrees and courses ==\nThe college offers the following degrees and courses.\n\n* Senior Secondary\n** [[Intermediate of Arts]]\n** Intermediate of Science\n** Intermediate of Commerce \n* Bachelor's degree\n** [[Bachelor of Arts]]\n** [[Bachelor of Science]]\n==Campus==\n* The college having 5 acre land including building.\n== References ==\n\n\n{{Official website|http://rlsycollegeaurangabad.in/}}\n\n{{Magadh University}}\n\n[[Category:Colleges affiliated to Magadh University]]\n[[Category:1971 establishments in India]]\n[[Category:Educational institutions established in 1971]]\n[[Category:Universities and colleges in Bihar]]\n[[Category:Bhupendra Narayan Mandal University]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|degree college in Bihar}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date = March 2020}}\n{{Use Indian English|date = March 2020}}\n{{Infobox university\n| native_name = Ram Lakhan Singh Yadav College\n| image       =\n| motto       = \n| established = {{Start date and age|1971}}\n| affiliation = [[Magadh University]]\n| principal   = Dr. Vijay Kumar Sinha\n| address     = Yamuna Nagar Road (G.T Road) \n| city        = [[Aurangabad]]\n| state       = [[Bihar]]\n| country     = [[India]]\n| postalcode  = 824101\n| coordinates = \n| website     = {{URL|http://rlsycollegeaurangabad.in/}}\n}}\n'''RLSY College, Aurangabad''' also known as '''Ram Lakhan Singh Yadav College, Aurangabad''' is a degree college in [[Aurangabad district]]<ref>{{cite web|title=RLSY College|url=https://www.bhaskar.com/bihar/aurangabad/news/rlsy-college-principal39s-exit-020603-4076651.html|website=Bhaskar news|accessdate=9 March 2019}}</ref> of [[Bihar]], [[India]].It is a Constitute College of [[Magadh University]]<ref>{{cite web|title= constituent college|url=https://magadhuniversity.ac.in/list-of-constituent-colleges/|website=Magadh university}}</ref>. The college offers [[senior secondary education]] ,[[undergraduate degree]]s and [[Postgraduate degree]]s in arts, science and conducts some vocational courses.The college was established in 1971 by [[Ram Lakhan Singh Yadav]]<ref>{{cite web|title=establish history|url=https://schools.org.in/aurangabad-(bihar)/10340313303/ram-lakhan-singh-yadav-college-aurangabad.html|website=school org}}</ref>. It is a Constitute College of [[Magadh University]] [[Bodh Gaya]] in 1986.Concerned with freedom revolution and localized on the high-way (G.T. Road) and in the heart of district headquarter of Aurangabad, Ramlakhan Singh Yadav College, was established in 1971. Affected with political and social injustice, the establishment of Ramlakhan Singh Yadav College by the hands of backward class people. [[File:Yadav College.png|right|350px]]\n== Degrees and courses ==\nThe college offers the following degrees and courses.\n\n* Senior Secondary\n** [[Intermediate of Arts]]\n** Intermediate of Science\n** Intermediate of Commerce \n* Bachelor's degree\n** [[Bachelor of Arts]]\n** [[Bachelor of Science]]\n==Campus==\n* The college having 5 acre land including building. [[File:RLSYCollege.jpg|right|450px]]\n\n== References ==\n\n\n{{Official website|http://rlsycollegeaurangabad.in/}}\n\n{{Magadh University}}\n\n[[Category:Colleges affiliated to Magadh University]]\n[[Category:1971 establishments in India]]\n[[Category:Educational institutions established in 1971]]\n[[Category:Universities and colleges in Bihar]]\n[[Category:Bhupendra Narayan Mandal University]]\n", "name_user": "Vipinahir", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/RLSY_College_Aurangabad"}
